eov uses OpenSlide to read whole-slide image formats.

OpenSlide upstream project: https://openslide.org/
OpenSlide source repository: https://github.com/openslide/openslide

OpenSlide license
=================

OpenSlide is licensed under the GNU Lesser General Public License, version 2.1
(LGPL-2.1).

Compliance notes
================

- eov must keep OpenSlide dynamically linked on Linux.
- The AppImage packaging bundles the OpenSlide shared library as a shared
  object, not as a static library.
- The Flatpak packaging installs OpenSlide as a shared library module under the
  Flatpak app prefix, not by static linking it into the application binary.
- Source for OpenSlide can be obtained from the upstream project listed above.
- If this project ever ships local patches to OpenSlide itself, those patches
  must be made available to recipients under the LGPL-2.1 terms.

License text
============

See assets/linux/licenses/LGPL-2.1.txt for the corresponding LGPL-2.1 text.
